      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:38:52 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6703a9a39496d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6703abacda569.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a mod that replaces the barbarian set with the cloud outfit from Final Fantasy!&lt;br&gt;It-s dyeable and the outfit will change hair colors you can also dye back to original colors the armor has physics also comes with The Buster Sword model from Super Smash Bros. Ultimate. It is a standalone item that you can find somewhere within the world, it cannot be bought or crafted.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor SelectedElement"&gt;If you don't want to go find it on your own&lt;/span&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://i.imgur.com/AWczS41.png" target="_blank"&gt;here is the exact location&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Notable things about the mod:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Based on the two handed swords/claymores&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unbreakable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Custom blade beam based on the Wind Cleaver projectile (only fires when you swing with R)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;DOES NOT RESPAWN&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;-WARNING-&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;sword does not respawn (unless you start a new save, I think) after you pick it up the first time. If you don't want to lose it, don't drop it. It won't break however, so if you don't want to carry it around anymore, store it in your house.</description>
